rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e11e92a2b85f488731e48a34142d344d1a96328","tid":310063,"uid":81287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人咩都要搵教室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論自己定同行<br />\n<br />\n大家都係上網搵資料<br />\n好多教材<br />\n<br />\n畫畫好講訓練<br />\n同自我檢驗<br />\n<br />\n有呢d能力先會學得好<br />\n<br />\n連上網都懶<br />\n<br />\n玩幾個星期又收皮<br />\n你有幾多恆心阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都畫左五年，只係人一懶真係可以幾個月唔動筆，搵畫室都希望自己可以有進步同有d野束縛住自己咁"},{"pid":"40739fc6e315ef558eb11f70e8c586f3400c785d","tid":310063,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"買書或者搵人教1對1<br />\n<br />\n又或者睇畫師/漫畫家錄播畫圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://search.bilibili.com/all?keyword=JUMP流&amp;from_source=banner_search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearch.bilibili.com%2Fall%3Fkeyword%3DJUMP%E6%B5%81%26from_source%3Dbanner_search&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN6xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=67218f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://search.bilibili.com/all?keyword=JUMP流&amp;from_source=banner_search</a>"},{"pid":"fb8f7f75f5a4d6cd626ec4b74717b4185cf2d35b","tid":310063,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補習社已經洗哂腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上果D 睇咩人<br />\n<br />\n未必學到想知既野"},{"pid":"ab08d38c65d0b83b1c20332b5a989412abbafb63","tid":310063,"uid":117237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人咩都要搵教室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論自己定同行<br />\n<br />\n大家都係上網搵資料<br />\n好多教材<br />\n<br />\n畫畫好講訓練<br />\n同自我檢驗<br />\n<br />\n有呢d能力先會學得好<br />\n<br />\n連上網都懶<br />\n<br />\n玩幾個星期又收皮<br />\n你有幾多恆心阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都畫左五年，只係人一懶真係可以幾個月唔動筆，搵畫室都希望自己可以有進步同有d野束縛住自己咁</blockquote><br />\n出發點錯左<br />\n<br />\n如果一樣野你真係鍾意/有興趣<br />\n駛咩縛住？<br />\n<br />\n鍾意就會排除萬難抽時間出黎做<br />\n<br />\n除非純粹技術<br />\n如果唔係綁你係一間畫室都冇意思<br />\n<br />\n你應該係上網去forum 好多大型貼畫既<br />\n日日浦下同人交流<br />\n令到自己有新衝擊/意念<br />\n去試<br />\n<br />\n畫左五年，除非你係返工咁樣既頻率畫<br />\n如果唔係時間冇咩意思<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你係想搵一個窗口<br />\n可以一口氣解決你畫畫既問題<br />\n<br />\n但解鈴還需繫鈴人<br />\n只可以靠自己<br />\n<br />\n最多係同人交流<br />\n咁樣網路已經幫你貼左好多step<br />\n<br />\n無論古至今<br />\n好既畫家都冇咩好既個人老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}